  [Text] Liu Wei-chung and Tung Chia-yao, the district 
prosecutors in charge of narcotics cases of the Shih-lin 
District Prosecutor's Office, and criminal investigation police 
of the first precinct cracked a big drug trafficking ring, which 
smuggled heroin from Thailand, on [words indistinct] in Taipei 
