Yanggang provinces should steadily enhance their contacts and 
broaden the field of economic and trade cooperation. An 
Kyu-sop, head of the Korean delegation, expressed that he will 
make all-out efforts to continuously carry forward the 
friendship between DPRK and China and to enhance the bilateral 
economic and trade cooperation. 

