<H3> <TI>   Li Ruihuan Tours Antwerp, Meets Mayor </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Li Ruihuan Tours Antwerp, Meets Mayor </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW2105233694 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese 0224 
GMT 21 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> OW2105233694 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service </F>
<F P=105>  Chinese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [By reporter Kang Xinwen (1660 2450 2429)] </F>
  [Text] Brussels, 20 May (XINHUA) -- Li Ruihuan, chairman 
of the National Committee of the Chinese People's Political 
Consultative Conference who is visiting here, drove to visit 
Belgium's northern port city Antwerp on 20 May. 
  Antwerp Mayor (Kors) welcomed Chairman Li Ruihuan and made 
an 
ebullient and friendly speech at a ceremony in the City Hall. 
(Kors) said: Antwerp is a small city with a population of less 
than 500,000, but it maintains good, cooperative relations with 
the "largest country" in the world. It received such 
distinguished Chinese guests as former President Li Xiannian and 
President Jiang Zemin. Now it is a great pleasure for the 
government and the people of Antwerp city to have the 
opportunity to receive Chairman Li Ruihuan. 
  (Kors) said: Since Antwerp established a friendly-city 
relationship with Shanghai in 1984, the two sides have increased 
exchanges and enhanced cooperation in the economic, trade, 
scientific, technological and cultural fields day by day. To 
date, almost all big companies and enterprises in Antwerp have 
set up branches or offices in Shanghai or other Chinese cities. 
Among them, the Bell Telephone Manufacturing Company has 
entered a very successful cooperation with Shanghai, and their 
cooperation may be called a model. (Kors) expressed the belief 
that Chairman Li's current visit will further promote the 
cooperation between the two countries in economic, trade, 
cultural and other fields. 
  Li Ruihuan said in his speech: Antwerp is a world famous, 
major port. With advanced diamond, electronics, 
telecommunications, chemical, pharmaceutical, and shipbuilding 
industries, it holds a very important position in Belgium's 
economic life. 
  Li Ruihuan was satisfied with the friendship and cooperation 
between Antwerp and Shanghai. He said: Since Antwerp 
established a friendly-city relationship with Shanghai, the two 
cities not only have constantly promoted economic cooperation 
and trade and cultural exchanges between them, but they have 
also made important contributions to promoting the political, 
economic, trade, scientific and technological, and cultural 
relations between China and Belgium. While China has entered a 
new stage of development in reform, opening up, and economic 
construction, Li Ruihuan hoped that Antwerp would fully play a 
leading role in further promoting the mutually-beneficial and 
cooperative relations between the two countries. 
  Then, Li Ruihuan, accompanied by officials of relevant 
departments of Belgium and Antwerp, visited the Bell Telephone 
Manufacturing Company and the Belgium Diamond Center, and toured 
Antwerp harbor. 

</TEXT>

