<H3> <TI>   Li Ruihuan Returns to Beijing From Europe </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Li Ruihuan Returns to Beijing From Europe </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW2205034394 Beijing XINHUA in English 0318 GMT 22 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW2205034394 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, May 22 (XINHUA) -- Li Ruihuan, chairman of 
the National Committee of the Chinese People's Political 
Consultative Conference (CPPCC), returned here by special plane 
this morning after his successful official goodwill visits to 
Finland, Sweden, Norway, Denmark and Belgium. 
  Li and his party were met at the great hall of the people by 
Hu Jintao, a Standing Committee member of the Political Bureau 
of the Central Committee of the Communist Party of China; Wu 
Xueqian, Wang Zhaoguo, Zhu Guangya and Wan Guoquan, 
vice-chairmen of the National Committee of the CPPCC, and other 
leading members of the parties and departments concerned. 
  Among those who had accompanied Li on the visit and arrived 
here by the same plane were Zhu Xun, secretary-general of the 
CPPCC National Committee; Liu Feng, a CPPCC National Committee 
member and chairman of the Zhejiang Provincial Committee of the 
CPPCC; Mei Xiangming, a Standing Committee member of the CPPCC 
National Committee and vice-chairman of the China Association 
for Promoting Democracy. 
  Diplomatic envoys of the five countries here were also on 
the 
occasion in the Great Hall of the People. 

</TEXT>

