<F P=102>   HK2205054694 Guangzhou Guangdong People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 1000 GMT 13 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> HK2205054694 </F>
<F P=104>  Guangzhou Guangdong People's Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Mandarin </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] While developing its economy fairly rapidly last 
year, Shenzhen has continued this year to maintain a good 
economic operations. It has been learned that during the first 
quarter of this year, Shengzhen's GDP reached 8.817 billion 
yuan, and its industrial production output value reached 11.562 
billion yuan, an increase of 21.3 and 33.9 percent respectively 
over the same period last year. 

</TEXT>

