<H3> <TI>   Hohhot-Beijing-Dandong Air Route Begins Service </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Hohhot-Beijing-Dandong Air Route Begins Service </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK2105024694 Hohhot NEIMENGGU RIBAO in Chinese 8 May 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> SK2105024694 </F>
<F P=104>  Hohhot NEIMENGGU RIBAO </F>
<F P=105>  Chinese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Summary] From 5 May, the Inner Mongolia branch of Air 
China opened an air route from Hohhot to Dandong via Beijing. 
  A Britain-made BAe-146 passenger plane makes the round trip 
every Thursday. The plane takes off in Beijing at 1455, arrives 
in Dandong at 1630, and starts to fly back to Beijing from 
Dandong at 1730. 

</TEXT>

