<F P=100> Northeast Region </F>
<H3> <TI>   Jilin Holds Disease Prevention, Control Day </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Jilin Holds Disease Prevention, Control Day </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK2105032694 Changchun JILIN RIBAO in Chinese 6 May 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> SK2105032694 </F>
<F P=104>  Changchun JILIN RIBAO </F>
<F P=105>  Chinese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The first national day on "Prevention and Control of 
Iodine-Deficient Diseases" fell on 5 May. On 5 May, more than 
600 people in Changchun took to the streets to conduct the 
propaganda on prevention and control of iodine-deficient 
diseases. Six cars were mobilized to help conduct the 
propaganda. More than 30 propaganda centers were set up on the 
streets. More than 100,000 copies of propaganda bills were 
distributed. Papers carrying more than 100 propaganda items 
were published. More than 150 banners with such slogans were 
carried. 
  It was informed that our province is one of the areas with 
serious iodine-deficient diseases. The first general 
investigation made in 1978 showed that 58 counties (cities) in 
the province had areas with iodine-deficient diseases, 750,000 
people or 5.6 percent of the people in the province suffered 
endemic goiter, about 70 percent of the people in the villages 
where these diseases were seriously spread suffered the 
diseases, and 0.22 percent of the people suffered cretinism. So 
far, our province has 270,000 patients suffering endemic goiter 
and more than 2,000 patients suffering cretinism. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

