<H3> <TI>   Li Lanqing Meets Singapore's Goh Chok Tong, Lee Kuan Yew </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Li Lanqing Meets Singapore's Goh Chok Tong, Lee Kuan Yew </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW2105055594 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese 1630 
GMT 19 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> OW2105055594 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service </F>
<F P=105>  Chinese </F>


